Build ID: wtp-20070419

Steps To Reproduce:
1. Create a dynamic web project, select "JavaServer Faces v1.1 Project" from the "Configurations" list.
2. Click "Next" button three times and setup JSF capabilities.
3. Click Finish.
4. Create a jsp file, open it with "Web Page Editor"
5. Drop a component onto the page from the "JSF HTML" palette drawer.
6. Press Ctrl and click the link "http://java.sun.com/jsf/core". jsf_core.tld will be opened.
7. Don't close jsf_core.tld, go back the jsp file and do the step 6 again.
